                <div2>
                    <p>A facsimile edition of <hi rend="u">ALL RELIGIONS are ONE</hi> has been published by
the Trianon Press for the William Blake Trust. The reproduction is by color collotype with the occasional
addition, by hand, of water-color washes through the stencils. To obtain a faithful reproduction, the entire
text was silhouetted by hand on the collotype negatives. The facsimile is printed on pure rag. Price: Â£ 18 or
$43.20.</p>
